{"article_id":"mwjW1amUXZhkwvGE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The New York Times is facing blowback","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"after its executive editor admitted to removing a controversial passage in a story","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"focusing on a 1993 sexual assault allegation against presumptive Democratic presidential nominee Joe Biden","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Joe BidenBiden assembling White House transition team Manchin","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"to back Biden for president","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Joe Biden must pick a progressive black woman as VP","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"if he wants to win MORE .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"The criticism comes","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"after the Times published an article","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"looking into allegations","depth":13},{"id":10,"text":"made against Biden by Tara Reade ,","depth":13},{"id":11,"text":"who says","depth":13},{"id":12,"text":"the then-senator sexually assaulted her","depth":14},{"id":13,"text":"when she worked as a Biden senate staffer .","depth":14},{"id":14,"text":"\" The Times found no pattern of sexual misconduct by Mr. Biden , beyond the hugs , kisses and touching","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":16,"text":"women previously said","depth":14},{"id":17,"text":"made them uncomfortable , \"","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"read the original passage in a Sunday story","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"before it was removed .","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"Times executive editor Dean Baquet told the news organization ' s media columnist Ben Smith","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"that the edit was made","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"because the Biden campaign argued","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"the phrasing made it appear that other women had made similar accusations against Biden .","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"\" The [ Biden ] campaign thought","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"that the phrasing was awkward","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"and made it look like","depth":15},{"id":27,"text":"there were other instances","depth":16},{"id":28,"text":"in which he had been accused of sexual misconduct , \"","depth":16},{"id":29,"text":"Baquet told Smith .","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"Smith then pressed Baquet on","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"why the Times didn ' t acknowledge the change in an editor 's note to readers .","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"\" We didn ' t think","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"it was a factual mistake .","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"I thought","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"it was an awkward phrasing issue","depth":16},{"id":36,"text":"that could be read different ways","depth":16},{"id":37,"text":"and that it wasn ' t something factual","depth":16},{"id":38,"text":"we were correcting , \"","depth":16},{"id":39,"text":"Baquet said .","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"Smith also raised questions","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"about whether Biden was being treated differently in the Times coverage than Supreme Court Justice Brett Kavanaugh","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Brett Michael KavanaughDemocratic challenger outraises Collins in Maine Senate race","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"NY Times faces blowback for removal of controversial passage on Biden sexual assault allegation","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"Wisconsin Democrats chair bashes Supreme Court decision on voting :","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"' I am about to explode '","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"MORE ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"who faced allegations of sexual assault during his confirmation process in 2018 .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Smith ' s story ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"titled , \" The Times Took 19 Days","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"to Report an Accusation Against Biden .","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"Here ' s Why , \"","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"asks","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"why the paper wrote about Kavanaugh accuser Julie Swetnick 's allegations the same day","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"they were made","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"without any independent corroboration ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"while the Times waited 19 days","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"before publishing a piece on Reade ' s accusations .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"\" Kavanaugh was already in a public forum in a large way , \"","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"answered Baquet ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"who argued","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"claims against the then-nominee were already in the public forum .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"\" If you ask the average person in America ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"they didn ' t know about the Tara Reade case , \"","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Baquet continued .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"\" We needed to introduce it with some reporting and perspective ...","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"and help people understand what to make of a fairly serious allegation against a guy","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"who had been a vice president of the United States","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"and was knocking on the door","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"of being his party ' s nominee . \"","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"Swetnick ' s claims were dismissed by an incredulous Kavanaugh as `` a joke '' during Senate confirmation hearings in October 2018 ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"while Sen. Susan Collins","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Susan Margaret CollinsThe Hill 's Campaign Report :","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"200 days to Election Day 2020 Democratic challenger outraises Collins in Maine Senate race","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Trump taps members of Congress","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"to advise on reopening MORE","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"( R-Maine )","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"called Swetnick 's claims \" outlandish ...","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"put forth","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"without any credible supporting evidence , \"","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"adding ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"\" that such an allegation can find its way into the Supreme Court confirmation process is a stark reminder","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"about why the presumption of innocence is so ingrained in our American consciousness . ''","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"NBC News contacted four people","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"Swetnick said","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"could corroborate her story .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"One could not recall","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"who Swetnick was ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"one other person was dead ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"and two did not respond to requests for comment ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"per NBC News .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"Reaction to the Smith interview of Baquet was swift across the political spectrum ,","depth":4},{"id":92,"text":"with Smith being praised for the questioning .","depth":4},{"id":93,"text":"In NYT , @ benyt asks top editor Dean Baquet some excellent questions about paper 's Tara Reade coverage versus its Kavanaugh coverage .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"Gets weak and sometimes laughable answers .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"https : //t.co/2vJpYv5HRr","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"pic.twitter.com/fb3BpXxT1N","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"- Byron York","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"( @ ByronYork )","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"April 13 , 2020","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"Another good day","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"not to be the NYT public editor","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"https : //t.co/Wpvo0fePgZ","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"- Margaret Sullivan","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"( @ Sulliview )","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"April 13 , 2020","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"Excellent @ benyt interview of NYT Executive Editor Dean Baquet on","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"why the paper took so long","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"to report on Tara Reade 's allegations against Joe Biden , how they did the reporting , and why they changed the text afterward .","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"Great to see Ben doing this stuff :","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"https : //t.co/TmJI5P4d84","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"- Glenn Greenwald","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"( @ ggreenwald )","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"April 13 , 2020","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Good for @ bensmith","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"for asking Dean Baquet","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"why the NYT covered an accusation against Kavanaugh far more aggressively than an accusation against Biden .","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"Baquet ' s answer","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"that Kavanaugh was more in the public forum than Biden","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"is ... quite lacking .","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"https : //t.co/F1t4qgLpOX","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"- Elise Jordan","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"( @ Elise_Jordan )","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"April 14 , 2020","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"This was quite revealing .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"Kudos to @ benyt","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"for really pressing Dean Baquet on the possible double standard with respect to Biden and Kavanaugh .","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"https : //t.co/hOw5mPXOUD","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"- Robby Soave","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"( @ robbysoave )","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"April 14 , 2020","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"Good news , guys .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"Apparently the 2020 primary is not a \" public forum in a large way \" or a \" live ongoing story \"","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"https : //t.co/MrsVSco2gj","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"pic.twitter.com/gTm5fv3eEo","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"- Rachael Larimore","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"( @ RachaelBL )","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"April 14 , 2020","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"Remember","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"the press spent a month","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"essentially arguing","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"that underage drinking was evidence","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"that Kavanaugh committed sexual assault ,","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"but a long pattern of `` hugs , kisses , and touching","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"that women previously said","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"made them uncomfortable ''","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"proves Biden 's innocence .","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"pic.twitter.com/CPGr48o8nK","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"( ( ( AG ) ) )","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"( @ AGHamilton29 )","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"April 12 , 2020","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"Smith joined The New York Times in 2020","depth":2},{"id":153,"text":"after being founding BuzzFeed eight years prior .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":307,"left":305,"right":306,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":305,"left":244,"right":304,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":244,"left":160,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":156,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":0,"right":155,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":157,"right":158,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":235,"right":242,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":200,"right":234,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":196,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":7,"right":195,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":191,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":171,"right":190,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":165,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":8,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":161,"right":163,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":